text: Aleksey Shibko (born 27 September 1977) is a Belarusian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Belarus Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
